<p>We process personal data under the following lawful bases:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Consent</strong> — for newsletters and analytics (you may withdraw consent at any time).</li>
<li><strong>Contract / legitimate interest</strong> — where needed to respond to your inquiry or provide services you requested.</li>
</ul>


<h2>Cookies & tracking</h2>
<p>We use cookies and similar technologies. Non-essential cookies (analytics and third-party trackers) will only be activated after you give explicit consent via the cookie banner. Essential cookies required for the site to function may be set without consent.</p>


