<h2>Retention</h2>
<p>We retain personal data only as long as necessary for the purposes described. For newsletter subscribers we retain contact data until you request deletion or unsubscribe.</p>


<h2>Your rights</h2>
<p>Under GDPR you have the right to:</p>
<ul>
<li>Access your personal data</li>
<li>Request rectification</li>
<li>Request erasure ("right to be forgotten")</li>
<li>Restrict or object to processing</li>
<li>Data portability</li>
<li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
</ul>
<p>To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@melwy.com">info@melwy.com</a>. You also have the right to lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority in the EU.</p>
